- ğŸ¯ **Risk Management**: Kelly Criterion, drawdown protection, position sizing
- ğŸ“ˆ **Live Trading**: Paper trading and live execution support
- ğŸ—ï¸ **Enterprise Architecture**: Clean Architecture + Domain-Driven Design
- ğŸ”’ **Type-Safe**: 100% type hints with mypy strict mode
