- ğŸ“Š **Monitoring**: Prometheus metrics for production deployment
- ğŸ’¾ **Database**: PostgreSQL with async support
- âš¡ **Async**: Non-blocking I/O throughout
- ğŸ¨ **CLI**: Beautiful command-line interface with Typer

